    HOW TO USE
    1) In Google Forms, click: Send ➜ <> (Embed HTML) ➜ Copy the iframe src URL
    2) Replace the src value below (YOUR_GOOGLE_FORM_EMBED_URL) with your Google Form embed link
       It will look like: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/FORM_ID/viewform?embedded=true
    3) Save this file as index.html and host it anywhere (GitHub Pages, Netlify, Vercel, etc.)
    4) In Make.com, use a Google Sheets ➜ Watch Responses trigger (linked to the same Form)
       OR use Google Forms ➜ Watch Responses (if available on your plan), then continue your scenario.
  -->
