          <li style="margin:8px 0;">In <strong>Make.com</strong>, create a scenario and add the trigger <em>Google Sheets → Watch Responses</em> (or <em>New Row</em>). Connect the same response sheet.</li>
          <li style="margin:8px 0;">Map your fields to the next modules (e.g., Gmail, Drive, Webhooks, etc.).</li>
          <li style="margin:8px 0;">Click <strong>Run once</strong>, submit a test via this page, confirm data arrives, then <strong>Turn on scheduling</strong>.</li>
